hotel_data.hotel_important_information:
Please note that the spa is closed from 27 April until 14 May.
Please inform Sheraton Milan Malpensa Airport Hotel & Conference Centre in advance of your expected arrival time. You can use the Special Requests box when booking, or contact the property directly with the contact details provided in your confirmation.
hotel_data.hotel_description: Sheraton Milan Malpensa Hotel is located inside Malpensa Airport's Terminal 1. It offers air-conditioned rooms with minibar and flat-screen TV. A fitness centre is also available. Rooms at Sheraton Milano Malpensa Airport Hotel and Conference Centre are soundproofed and feature Sheraton Sweet Sleeper beds. Other hotel facilities include business meeting rooms, a spa and beauty centre and indoor swimming pool. Guests can sip a cocktail at the on-site bar and have dinner at the restaurant, which specialises in Italian cuisine. The hotel is a 40-minute drive from Milan centre, and 40 km from Rho Fiera Milano Exhibition Centre. You can also use public and private shuttles to Milan Central Railway Station.
hotel_data.hotelier_welcome_message:
The Sheraton Milan Malpensa Airport Hotel & Conference Center is the only hotel with direct access inside the Terminal 1 of Malpensa's Airport and only 30 minutes away from the city center, both by car and by the Malpensa Express train. With 433 rooms, including 19 suites and 58 Club Room, it is the perfect choice for all those who need to stay overnight between flights and rest in the comfortable Sweet Sleeper Beds.
The Sheraton Milan Malpensa is an Hotel with a new architectonical and logistic concept, which means a building with a unique design. It is one of the biggest Conference Center in Italy with up to 30 soundproof meeting rooms fitting every meeting or event needs.
It is also possible to enjoy a Mediterranean meal or a refreshing cocktail at the Moterosa Bar or taste the Italian specialities at Il Canneto Restaurant.
Moreover, guests can enjoy the Shine Spa at the first floor with 1000sqm beauty center and its indoor swimming pool. Its certified therapists will help you to renew mind, body and spirit.
